original_text: For who in the heaven can be compared unto the Lord? who among the sons of the mighty can be likened unto the Lord?
korean_text: 무릇 구름 위에서 능히 여호와와 비교할 자 누구며 신들 중에서 여호와와 같은 자 누구리이까

sentences.original_text: can be compared unto the Lord?
who among the sons of the mighty
can be likened unto the Lord?
